.TH XIL\-ASSEMBLE "1" "2026\-04\-24" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-assemble
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-assemble
[-h] (--episode EPISODE | --tag TAG) [--show SHOW] [--output OUTPUT] [--parsed PARSED] [--gap-ms GAP_MS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Audio Assembly — assemble voice stems into master MP3

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S01E01) — derives cast config path

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01)

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,OUTPUT\/\fR
Output master MP3 path (default: <slug>_<TAG>_master.mp3)

.TP
\fB\-\-parsed\fR \fI\,PARSED\/\fR
Path to parsed script JSON (default: parsed/parsed_<slug>_<TAG>.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-gap\-ms\fR \fI\,GAP_MS\/\fR
Silence gap between foreground stems in ms (default: 600)

